The information contained in the telephone directory records are the name, phone number and address of the person whose record is entered in the telephone directory system project 
in C++. So, the simple file handling cum telephone directory operations users can perform in this project are: 
•Add telephone record[Text Wrapping Break]
•Show records[Text Wrapping Break]
•Modify record[Text Wrapping Break]
•Search telephone records[Text Wrapping Break]
•Delete record
